On January 18 , Alibaba held a high-level dialogue session in Chongqing , announcing that by exploring a new model of " Internet + Poverty Eradication " , it would help promote accurate poverty alleviation and rural rejuvenation .
This is after putting forward the rural strategy , launching the rural Taobao project , on-line Xingnong poverty alleviation platform , the establishment of Alibaba poverty relief fund , Ali once again " added code " to the fight against poverty .
Getting rid of poverty is one of the most important national strategies in China today .
The total eradication of poverty has never been realized in China for thousands of years .
" E-commerce poverty alleviation is a new round of anti-poverty development innovative measures , is the realization of accurate poverty alleviation , accurate out of poverty an important grasp .
The central government attaches great importance to and points out that it can play the role of the Internet in helping to get rid of poverty , promote precise poverty alleviation , and get agricultural products out of the countryside through the Internet . "
As a result , Ali proposed a rural strategy as early as 2014 , along with large data cloud computing and globalization , and listed as Ali's three core strategies for the next 20 years .
In the same year , Ali launched a rural Taobao ( Village Taobao ) project to recruit " village sophomore " in the countryside , leading farmers to get rich through electricity merchants .
In 2017 , Ali worked with the commercial sector to build an anti-poverty channel for agriculture and agriculture . At present , he has docked 13 provinces and 120 state-level poverty-stricken counties .
Ali platform spawned Taobao village , already has 2118 .
Of these , nearly 400 appeared in the poverty-stricken counties of the province and 33 in the poverty-stricken counties of 13 countries .
In 2017 , in Alibaba China retail platform , the national Taobao village sales reached 120 billion yuan .
Mr Zhang said that in the face of a national strategy to combat poverty , Ali had been thinking about how to use the innovative capabilities of Ali's economy , such as technology , big data and cloud computing , to make a new way out of poverty .
Among them , village Taobao is the main load-bearing platform for Ali electric merchants to get out of poverty , and went through a direct-selling Internet to get out of poverty new link .
In the planting link , the village Taobao and the ant gold clothing jointly carry out agricultural capital agricultural tools and small loan support .
In 2017 , of the 832 state-level poverty-stricken counties , ant gold clothing served 795 , providing them with convenient payment , credit and other services .
The rookie solves warehousing and logistics , the day cat is responsible for sales , Ali Yun's large data feed back to guide agricultural production , further improve the supply standard , quality and market competitiveness of agricultural products .
The development of electric business out of poverty requires not only products , sales channels , industrial planning , but also talents .
By offering e-commerce courses at Taobao University , Ali taught farmers standardization , quality and large-scale planting methods , and realized the combination of " help-the-poor " and " help-the-mind " so as to keep farmers out of poverty on a sustainable basis .
These courses already cover about 92 % of state-level poverty-stricken counties .
But " commonweal mentality , commercial means " the thought of getting out of poverty , also can guarantee Ali in the help-the-poor time to achieve " true help-the-poor " .
Ma Yun , chairman of Alibaba's board of directors , once said that poverty eradication should be divided into three stages : poverty alleviation , poverty eradication and enrichment .
Poverty alleviation is to teach people to fish , to get rid of poverty is to teach people to fish , to get rich is to create a " fish pond " for farmers , so that farmers can have fish to feed .
Electric business-driven industry to help the poor , is to build fish pond .
In the industry help-the-poor , Ali and Shaanxi Luochuan cooperation to create the Luochuan apple industry anti-poverty model , has been the relevant departments as an example of replication and promotion throughout the country .
Ali electricity business poverty alleviation work has also been recognized by the decision-making level .
Alibaba as the representative of the e-commerce enterprises have been posted , through the online channel , to ensure that farmers increase production and increase income .
Some village sophomore and ant gold workers have also been invited to the United Nations and Africa to share the experience of electricity merchants getting out of poverty .
At present , the China Office of the United Nations World Food Programme , together with the village Taobao , in Anhui and other places to carry out e-commerce industries to help the poor .
Sina Financial News was held on January 16 by Zhang Li , director of the Institute of Electrical Businessmen of the Ministry of Commerce , and co-organised by the Ali Research Institute and the China Vision think-tank , the Third Congress of the New Economic think-tank , which was held on January 16 , and delivered a speech by Zhang Li , director of the Research Institute of the Ministry of Commerce .
She believes that our globalization actually ignores the most important issues , that is , the body and use of globalization , and the stage of globalization .
In this way , many people believe that globalization has stagnated , and that many developed and developing countries , in the new stage , have different attitudes towards globalization , which is different from the model .
The second concept is the question of the medium-term phase of globalization . What are the constraints on the medium-term phase of globalization ?
Restricted by the economic environment foundation , it is precisely because the economic base has changed the globalization has been restricted .
Zhang Li believes that the global economic adjustment at the end of 2017 basically ended , after 2018 will enter a new round of growth period , the next round of growth must be driven by raw products .
