Total sales again record-breaking growth rate back to the accelerated track
Since 2006 , China's online retail sales can be said to have been showing super-fast growth , it is estimated that at that time the online shopping is very fresh , do not go out can also buy things , too cool !
But since 2013 , online retail growth has started to fall below 50 % , for the first time below 40 % in 2015 and 26.2 % in 2016 .
But things are different this year , with online retail sales accelerating again , with growth rebounding to 34.2 % in January-September .
Much higher than the growth rate in 2015 and 2016 .
Maybe people go for a walk around and find it more enjoyable to buy or buy .
Among them , physical goods online retail sales of nearly 5.08 trillion yuan , service online retail sales of nearly 1.49 trillion yuan .
The proportion of total retail sales of social goods reached 13.6 percent , an increase of nearly 3 percentage points year-on-year .
