It is not uncommon for a film to go from preparation to release for a year or two or even a few years .
Animated film " Big Fish Begonia " recently announced that it will be released on July 8 , from the preparation to the release of the film for 12 years !
" Big Fish Begonia " original author Liang Jun , 21 - year-old from Tsinghua University thermal power professional study , and close friend Zhang Chun created the other side of the sky , in 2008 won a million-dollar venture capital , launched the animation film debut " Big Fish Begonia " .
The film has won many awards at home and abroad in the creative sample stage , and has been included and praised as " one of the most outstanding works of art " by the Pompidou Contemporary Art Centre in France .
Since it took six years from creativity to production , the film has been known by millions of fans looking forward to its release as a " pit of the gods " .
" Big Fish Begonia " tells a fantasy story that belongs to the Chinese . With the release of the trailer , it brings new expectations to all viewers .
" I've only done this for 12 years , and now it's gone from a dream to a reality . I'm nervous and excited , " Liang said .
" I'm going to drive the team crazy trying to use one-fifths of someone else's budget to make exactly the same picture as everyone else , " Zhang said .
The 3 - D Family Animation Film " Bean Fook " premiere in Wuhan on 25 , " Bean Fook " director Zou , " Bean Fook " animation director Meng wisdom , film music producer , Emmy Award winner Tom Disher all appeared on the scene to share the behind-the-scenes story of the film creation .
From the story of Liu An , the king of Huainan in the Han Dynasty in Chinese traditional culture , he was born out of the traditional allusions of " Liu An made bean curd , made by mistake " and told the story of the hero , " Bean Fu " , who was transformed from a bean into a human figure , overcame many difficulties and persisted in practicing fairy dreams . The film is deeply rooted in the local culture of Hubei Province .
Wudang Mountain in Shiyan City , Hubei Province , is one of the world's cultural heritage sites announced by the United Nations , as well as the birthplace of Taoist culture and Wudang Wushu , known as " the never-ending win-win situation , the first fairy mountain in the world " .
Director Zou revealed that in the early stage of the film creation , he and the main creative team went to Wudang Mountain to gather the wind .
He said that the story of " Bean Fu " took place during the reign of Emperor Wudi of the West Han Dynasty . Under the background of Emperor Liu An of Huainan , the protagonist of the film , " Bean Fu " , was a bean that accidentally turned into a human form when Liu An was refining Dan .
In addition to Wudang Mountain , the birthplace of Taoist culture , Hubei also has a deep origin with China's long-standing traditional musical instrument , the bell .
