According to the Market Star report , from 2005 to 2011 , the GDP of our province rose from the middle to the bottom of the table in one fell swoop .
However , there are still some difficulties in the economic growth of our province , such as low investment efficiency and lack of core competitiveness of the industrial economy . Therefore , the latest issue of the Economic Blue Page of the Provincial Economic Information Center suggests improving the quality and efficiency of economic growth .
Based on some representative indicators of the economy of our province in 2005 and 2011 , it is compared with the whole country and the central region .
In terms of industrial economic benefits , in 2011 , a considerable proportion of high energy-consuming industries such as industrial energy and raw materials in our province were affected by market fluctuations and " double pressure " of overcapacity . At the same time , the lack of innovation in leading industries such as home appliances and automobiles resulted in meagre profits .
But the large amount of investment did not bring the corresponding economic benefits , it is the important reason that causes the economic growth quality and the benefit of our province is not high .
In this regard , experts suggest that effective measures should be taken to encourage enterprise innovation , and the scientific and technological achievements of universities and scientific research institutes should also be transferred to enterprises in a timely manner .
For the industrial economic benefits are not high , experts said , we should also actively promote industrial merger and reorganization , optimize the industrial layout , and extend the industrial chain .
July 26 : On July 22 , the reporter learned from the Hongqiao District that the city's largest along the river zonal park , Hongqiao District South Canal on both sides of the green landscape upgrading works completed and free of charge to open to the public .
Based on the advantages of natural ecology and historical and cultural resources , the whole landscape belt has re-planned and upgraded the two sides of the South Canal to create five river views along the West Corridor of the West Corridor of the West Corridor of Xintiandi Street , Wellington Square , Tianzi Jindu Site Park .
About 1,500 metres of plastic walkway was also laid in the riverside green space between Jinhua Bridge and the new three-stone bridge , with distance marks on the walkway .
In addition to planting a variety of flowers and trees on both sides of the corridor , a children's playground has been built , and a number of groups of sculpture sketches have been set up .
It can be found that the shore has also built seats , walkways , bridges , pro-level platforms and sand pools for children to play with , so as to integrate the green landscape and water systems on both sides of the Straits , providing another good place for leisure , fitness and entertainment for the public .
