New Measures of " Dissolution of Colleges and Universities " in Beijing : Tens of thousands of teachers and students from the North Chemical Industry will be admitted to the new campus in Changping
The opening ceremony of the new campus of Beijing Chemical University was held on the 2nd in Changping District , Beijing , and the 1,800 - acre green campus was officially put into use .
The reporter learned from the ceremony that in recent years , in order to strengthen the core functions of the capital and manage the " disease of big cities " , under the background of the coordinated development of Beijing-Tianjin-Hebei and the elimination of non-capital functions , Beijing has accelerated the development of the central city colleges and universities to the suburbs , and some university teachers and students are gradually moving to the new campuses of Shunyi , Daxing , Fangshan and other suburbs .
North chemical new campus is located in Changping Nankou Town , covering an area of 1800 mu , 40 kilometers from the urban area , is one of the key projects in Beijing to solve the non-capital functions .
The new campus is divided into three phases . At present , the first phase of construction has been completed . The second phase of construction is expected to be fully launched by the end of this year . Upon completion , the project will meet the needs of nearly 20,000 undergraduates , graduate students and faculty members for study and life .
May 29 , the first China Fireworks Safety and Environmental Protection Expo will be held in Liuyang .
The event revolves around the theme of " Science , Technology , Safety and Environmental Protection " for a period of two days . At that time , the most advanced firework machinery in the national fireworks industry , the most safe and environmentally friendly raw materials and new products will be gathered in Liuyang .
This Expo will invite a large number of experts , entrepreneurs , fireworks industry academic exchanges , share fireworks safety and environmental protection latest technological achievements .
Among them , the mechanized production equipment of fireworks and the display of safety and environmental protection products will be carried out in Dayao Town . The main exhibitors include the production of safety and environment-friendly personal discharge products such as drug-related machinery equipment , low sensitivity , low explosive energy , sulfur-free and micro-smoke .
At the same time , the display of fireworks safety and environmental protection products jointly sponsored by 16 fireworks enterprises in Liuyang will be divided into two stages : product selection and product display . The outstanding new products selected through the pre-selection will be displayed on the evening of May 29 at Liuyang City fireworks viewing platform and Jintan display site .
