Since the second half of 2009 , Xiaoshan flower and wood sales ( volume ) have maintained a high trend , especially this spring , Xiaoshan seedling sales hit a record high , sales have increased greatly , and prices have soared . According to statistics , from January to June this year , sales of seedlings in Xiaoshan area have increased by 48 % over the same period last year , the biggest increase in nearly 20 years .
Shi Haiyong , deputy director of the Forestry Bureau of Xiaoshan District , said that along with the good sales situation , Xiaoshan flower and wood production has also achieved a relatively rapid development .
In the past two years , the planting area of Xiaoshan flowers and trees has expanded by 30,000 mu , and the total area has reached 180,000 mu . At the same time , Xiaoshan Miao farmers have been actively developing outside the region , setting up 80,000 mu of flower and wood bases in various parts of the country , an increase of 30,000 mu over 2008 .
With the expansion of the planting area , the quality of the seedlings has been improved , the value of the nursery has been continuously improved , the large size and high quality of the seedlings have been retained more , and some of the seedlings have been reluctant to sell .
Shi Haiyong also reminded that in the face of the current boom in production and marketing , producers should be calm , objective analysis , not only to see the social demand for flowers and trees will be long-term , constantly increasing , but also to recognize that the market competition will be more intense .
