International Online News ( reporter Liu Pai ) : On the 18th , the Economic and Commercial Office of the Italian Embassy in China hosted the China-Italy Environmental Protection Fair . People from enterprises and scientific research institutes of the two countries exchanged views on the cooperation between the two countries in the field of renewable resources under the new situation and reached a positive consensus .
It is reported that the Chinese delegates mainly include China Renewable Resources Development Co . Ltd . , China International Technology Transfer Co-operation Network , while the Italian side is composed of the Global Energy and Environmental Exchange Organization , the Italian Bologna Regional Enterprise Federation and other organizations .
The representative said that Italy had diversified environmental technologies and solutions in the area of renewable resources , proposed pilot projects with China in the areas of industrial waste disposal , waste oil treatment and waste incineration equipment , and looked forward to extending its experience of environmental cooperation with China to other parts of the world .
This lets live in Nanning City democratic road machinery hall dormitory Gao aunt family is very happy .
Neighbors also said that it was rare to see the rich trees blossoming , and the residents of the neighborhood thought it was a very auspicious event , and they all came to see it with great interest .
Rich tree name " Malaba chestnut " , is a tropical plant , native to Mexico , like warm and humid , must be in the sun , water , nutrients and other conditions are appropriate , before the emergence of flowering phenomena .
Even in the wild , where tropical conditions are appropriate , the flowering of rich trees is rare and has been described as " only one-thousandth of the flowering rate " .
Yesterday morning , the reporter came to Nanning Democratic Road Machinery Hall dormitory , under the guidance of Aunt Gao , the reporter saw the rich tree .
Rich tree species in the community's flower beds , about 5 meters high , the thickest branches around about 30 centimeters , leaves green and lush .
Flowers on the top of the higher branches , blooming flowers more than 10 cm wide , light yellow filaments evenly spread , green buds split and curl on both sides , stamens as fine as silver , silk head Venus dot .
Aunt Gao told reporters that the tree had been a rich tree for eight years , when it was planted about 1 meter high , and now it is more than 5 meters long .
It was a bonsai that her son bought from the flower-and-bird market , and later planted in a flower bed , and she did not take care of it .
At 1710 hours today , the 119 Command Center in Shaoyang City received an alarm that a fire broke out in four-hydrogen furan stored in the Hongzhi Chemical Plant in Longsutang , Shuangqing District of the city .
Shaoyang City fire brigade immediately dispatched 5 squadron 20 fire engines carrying heavy anti-chemical clothing , anti-chemical washing vehicles and other equipment to the scene .
After preliminary investigation , the fire is a small storage tank of chemical substances such as tetrahydrofuran , which produces a large amount of smoke in the field .
Up to the time of the press release , fire officers and soldiers are nervous rescue , municipal health , safety supervision , environmental protection , public security , transportation and other departments have rushed to the scene , no casualties have been found .
Today , four groups , such as Tonglu County , Zhejiang Province , have been awarded the 8th China Environment Award for their contributions to beautiful China .
The China Environmental Award , which was established in 2000 , is the highest award in the field of environmental protection in China and is composed of a number of central departments .
Li Wei , head of the selection committee and secretary-general of the China Environmental Protection Foundation , said China is facing ecological problems left over from the previous decades of heavy GDP and light environmental protection development model .
The purpose of the award is to recognize those units and individuals who have contributed to improving the environment and people's livelihood in order to show respect for public opinion .
In the opinion of the selection committee , the eco-county-based TongLushan County of Zhejiang Province should receive this award .
