Yesterday , 11 - year-old Luo Shiyu and his mother came to the Three Gorges Square to pick up the rubbish around them and hand out leaflets to passers-by , hoping to arouse more people's awareness of protecting the environment .
Like Luo Shiyu's family , volunteers from 106 families from 24 street towns in Shapingba District took to the streets to act as " small guardians of environmental protection " .
Next , they will volunteer to do clean work in their neighborhood , or go into their homes to talk about environmental protection . The theme of the event is " Chuang Wei , hand in hand with the family " , which will end on June 20 , according to a report by the Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the People's Republic of China and the Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the People's Republic of China .
Zou Shoumin , director of the Environmental Supervision Bureau of the Ministry of Environmental Protection of China , said in Beijing on the 22nd that in August , 57 cases of day-to-day continuous punishment were implemented nationwide , and the newly revised Environmental Protection Law , which was implemented earlier this year , clearly added to China's environmental law enforcement efforts .
At present , environmental protection authorities in various parts of China may investigate and deal with environmental violations by means of day-to-day continuous punishment , seizure , production cut-off and transfer of administrative detention , and cooperate with the judicial organs in punishing environmental crimes .
Zou said that in August , a total of 335 cases of seizure and seizure were carried out in various parts of China ; 177 cases of limited production and suspension of production were implemented ; 189 cases of administrative detention were transferred , and 166 cases of suspected environmental pollution crimes were transferred .
Among them , Henan carries out 7 consecutive daily punishment , at present , China is from the end of control to the whole process of embedding , comprehensive environmental pollution control .
Although the downward pressure on the economy appears , the Ministry of Environmental Protection has previously made it clear that China should correctly handle the position of environmental protection in economic development and enhance its " green determination " . The more the economy grows , the less it will be able to relax environmental protection and give play to the optimized role of environmental protection in the economy .
The reporter learned from Hebei Kailuan Group that at 11 : 25 am on the 7th , there was an explosion in the emulsification workshop of Kailuan Group Chemical Co . , Ltd . , located in Tangshan City , Hebei Province , where 13 workers were trapped .
Up to now , of the 13 people trapped , one has been rescued , rushed to the hospital rescue , the remaining 12 are in intense search and rescue .
It is understood that at present the scene has been blocked , the local public security , fire , medical and other departments are on-site rescue .
According to eyewitnesses , there was a loud noise at the time of the incident , and a mushroom cloud rose into the sky in a flash of time .
According to the personnel of Kailuan Group , which organized on-site search and rescue , Tangshan Kailuan ( Group ) Chemical Co . , Ltd . is located in the north of Zhao Gaozhuang , Tangshan City , Hebei Province . It is a designated production enterprise of civil explosive equipment approved by the state . It was founded in 1958 and was formerly known as Kailuan Mining Bureau 6 O 2 Factory .
