Some experts believe that under the current situation , the new round of revitalization of the northeast industry is not only related to the national economic recovery , but also will have an impact on the long-term development of China's manufacturing industry and international competitiveness , so it is urgent to adjust the transformation .
It is the primary performance of the northeast industry in the current economic downturn that the traditional industry is losing more money in the raw material industry and heavy machinery and equipment manufacturing industry has suffered a serious decline or even a loss .
In the past in the economic downturn , mainly low-end , primary products by the impact of the characteristics , but this economic fluctuations , the Northeast traditional industry high-end , low-end industrial products are affected .
