Of these , 55 national-level environmental protection projects have won 132.46 million yuan for special state funds for environmental protection , 43 provincial-level environmental protection projects and 12.8 million yuan for special provincial-level environmental protection funds .
It is understood that the construction of the project involves comprehensive management of the regional water environment ( including protection of the ecological environment of the lake ) , environmental protection of drinking water sources , comprehensive improvement of the rural environment , pollution prevention and control of large-scale livestock and poultry breeding , pollution control of industrial enterprises and demonstration of eco-city construction .
