The Southern Daily News ( reporter / Xie Qingyu ) reporter learned from the Provincial Environmental Protection Department today that the results of the environmental protection credit rating for key pollution sources in Guangdong Province in 2012 are being announced .
After evaluation , 134 of the 1,251 enterprises listed in the environmental protection credit management list are temporarily not rated for reasons such as stopping production , non-acceptance , closure and so on .
In the proposed red card enterprises , mainly to electroplating , printing and dyeing , prevention and treatment of heavy pollution enterprises more , some sewage treatment plants are also on the list .
The Provincial Environmental Protection Department said that in order to reflect the principles of openness , fairness and impartiality and accept public supervision , the results of the ratings are now posted on the Environmental Protection Department's website .
During the publicity period , the Environmental Protection Department receives calls , letters and visits from the public . The Environmental Protection Department will investigate , verify and deal with the problems reflected .
