The report analyzed the results of a questionnaire survey of 1,045 foreign tourists who visited Seoul last December .
The report pointed out that the per-capita amount of shopping for foreign tourists was 1.06 million won .
Among them , the largest per capita shopping volume of Chinese tourists was 2.13 million won , 6.5 times that of Japanese tourists and 3.2 times that of US and European tourists .
