Limited purchase is a hard bar of many urban real estate regulation policy .
In May 2017 , Jinan issued a regulation that undergraduate students pay social security for half a year in a row , can enjoy the same purchase policy of local permanent residence residents ;
In June , Wuhan issued a policy requiring college students to settle down with their diplomas and employment permits within 3 years of graduation .
Subsequently , the policy added , the official said , " college students can buy a house at a price below 20 % of the market price " ;
In July , Chengdu issued a regulation that young people with bachelor's degree or above in foreign universities can apply to settle down in Chengdu with their graduation certificate .
In addition , there are Kunshan , Shanghai and other cities or regions also issued " talent introduction " related policies , to reduce the threshold for the purchase of talent .
Zhang Hongwei believes that this is actually the competition of the big cities for the population , especially the talent , to retain the population , especially the talent , the city is competitive , which is the most important significance of these real estate policies .
Some even argue that this means the time has come for a " buy-out " cancellation of the property market .
