Tourism amorous feelings of small town : amorous feelings how drunk tourists
Absrtact : The potential of a small town in Zhejiang has been awakened gradually .
Now these small towns have become an important destination for tourists to appreciate Zhejiang's landscape , read Zhejiang's culture and feel Zhejiang's homesickness . They will also provide important help to our province's efforts to create the most beautiful tourist destination of " Poetic Painting Zhejiang " in China .
Better than amorous feelings
" Social drama gongs and drums with the rise of the moon , sausage fragrance with the wind .
" Walking Shaoxing Anchang ancient town , can be seen everywhere hoop barrels , bamboo weaving , iron beating , shoes , lace picking , spinning cotton and other traditional handicraft skills , fully display the intangible cultural heritage of Anchang ancient town , the Quartet tourists enjoy the experience of Shaoxing folk customs , enjoy the atmosphere of Shaoxing historical and cultural accumulation .
It is reported that this year's New Year's Day three-day holiday period , Anchang ancient town visitors more than 65,000 .
In Zhejiang , such a unique town as Anchang Ancient Town is dotted with : Jiaxing Xitang's billows , flowing with the warmth of Jiangnan Water Township ; Quzhou 28 white wall Dewa , telling the vicissitudes of the thousand-year-old town ; Taizhou Shitang Town fishermen's paintings delineate the traditional and modern life of fishers .
In recent years , with the promotion of tourism construction in the whole region of our province , the potential of Zhejiang town has been awakened gradually .
In 2016 , the General Office of the provincial government officially promulgated the " Measures for the Implementation of the Establishment of Tourist Attractions in Zhejiang Province " , and proposed that about 100 provincial-level tourism towns with honest folk customs , beautiful ecological environment and rich tourism practices should be accepted and named in the province over a period of about five years .
Now these small towns have become an important destination for tourists to appreciate Zhejiang's landscape , read Zhejiang's culture and feel Zhejiang's homesickness . They will also provide important help to our province's efforts to create the most beautiful tourist destination of " Poetic Painting Zhejiang " in China .
The relevant person-in-charge of the provincial tourism bureau introduced that under the upsurge of the creation of the tourist amorous feelings town , the villages and towns in our province now attach more importance to the creation of the personalized tourism industry , new tourism projects and business conditions emerge in an endless stream , bringing rich experience to the tourists and winning a good word-of-mouth .
Focus on Promotion
