Throughout the world , the Dutch town of Lether , the Austrian town of Halstadt and the French town of Pumpkin , with tulips , " salt " and pumpkins as their core attractions , attracts a large number of tourists from all over the world each year to help the town's economy take off .
For the amorous feelings of the small town , the emphasis of " highlighting characteristics , retaining homesickness " makes the small town have obvious personality and soul , but also to provide cultural infiltration , carrying the local culture , to highlight the local civilization .
