Essentially , the small town of tourist amorous feelings is a compound open tourist scenic spot , and it should be the living space shared by the local residents and the foreign tourists and even the residents .
As the main battleground for the growth of tourism in the future , tourism-style towns are not only likely to change the ecological outlook of the countryside , the way of economic and social development and the direction of the flow of industrial elements , but also an important force to bridge the gap between urban and rural infrastructure and wake up the revival of rural culture .
