General Secretary of the CPC Central Committee and President Xi Jinping attended the opening ceremony of the high-level dialogue between the Communist Party of China and the world's political parties at the Great Hall of the People on December 1
Keynote speech entitled " Work together to build a better world "
Xi stressed that political parties should conform to the development trend of the times and grasp the trend of human progress
Willing to work with all parties to promote the sincere desire to build a community of human destiny
The political party plays an important role in the political life of the country and is also an important force in promoting the progress of human civilization .
At the end of the year , leaders of nearly 300 political parties and political organizations from around the world gathered in Beijing to discuss plans for cooperation .
Xi pointed out that the relevance of human life today is unprecedented , and the global problems facing mankind are unprecedented .
The future of the peoples of the world is more and more closely linked .
People all over the world should uphold the concept of the world , understand each other and seek common ground while reserving differences
Work together to build a community of human destiny
I put forward all the way around the initiative , is to carry out the concept of human destiny community .
Xi stressed that we should strive to build a world away from fear and universal security and adhere to a new security concept that is common , comprehensive , cooperative and sustainable .
We should strive to build a world far from closed , open and inclusive , adhere to the world is rich and colorful , civilization is a diverse concept .
Let all civilizations coexist in harmony .
We should strive to build a beautiful , clean and beautiful world , adhere to the concept of coexistence between man and nature , and work together to create a harmonious and livable
Human Home
We will establish a new type of political party relationship that seeks common ground while reserving differences , mutual respect and mutual learning .
We will build a network of exchanges and cooperation among international political parties in various forms and at various levels , bringing together the powerful forces of building a community of human destiny .
We must do our own thing well , which in itself is a contribution to the building of a community of human destiny .
We will also create more opportunities for the world by promoting China's development .
We do not import foreign models , we do not export Chinese models , and we do not require other countries to copy Chinese practices .
First
The Communist Party of China will , as always , contribute to world peace and tranquillity .
China will hold high the banner of peace , development , cooperation and win-win progress , unswervingly follow the path of peaceful development and actively promote the building of global partnership .
Take the initiative to participate in the process of political settlement of difficult issues in international hot spots .
No matter how far China develops , it will never seek hegemony and never engage in expansion .
By the middle of this century , China will build a strong , prosperous , democratic , civilized , harmonious and beautiful socialist modern country .
This will benefit the Chinese people as well as the people of all countries in the world .
We urge all political parties in the world to join us in creating more opportunities for cooperation for the world and striving to promote common development and prosperity for all countries in the world .
The Communist Party of China has always emphasized building a world perspective , actively learning from the achievements of civilization created by people from all over the world , and applying them in the light of China's reality .
We will carry out dialogue and exchanges and cooperation and support the people of all countries to strengthen cultural exchanges and civil friendship .
