On December 1st , General Secretary of the CPC Central Committee and President Xi Jinping delivered a keynote speech at the opening ceremony of the high-level dialogue between the Communist Party of China and the world political party
The future of the peoples of the world is more and more closely linked .
People all over the world should uphold the idea of the world and understand each other .
Representatives of foreign political parties present at the dialogue highly agree with Xi Jinping's idea of promoting the building of a community of human destiny and working together to build a better world .
Think
This shows the determination and commitment of the Communist Party of China to build a better world .
Strive to make this planet where we are born and grow into a harmonious family , and turn the aspirations of the peoples of the world for a better life into reality .
Facing the leaders of nearly 300 political parties and political organizations in the world , Xi Jinping systematically expounded the profound connotation of the human destiny community .
Xi Jinping points out , the world pattern is changing , the development pattern is changing .
All political parties should conform to the development trend of the times and develop themselves with the development of the country , the nation and the human race
As always , contribute to the common development of the world and , as always , contribute to the exchange of world civilization .
Xi Jinping's speech clearly stated China's commitment to the construction of the human destiny community and demonstrated the Chinese Communist Party as the world's largest political party in the world's feelings and responsibilities .
In his speech , Li said that at the Astana summit in June this year , President Xi Jinping reached important consensus with all parties on consolidating unity and mutual trust , strengthening security cooperation , docking development strategy and deepening cultural exchanges .
After the summit , China took over the rotating presidency .
With the active support of all parties , we will promote the steady development of cooperation in all fields .
Li Keqiang put forward the following suggestions on building a regional national destiny community .
First , create a safe and stable regional environment .
Second , accelerate the development of strategic docking cooperation .
Development is an effective way to deal with regional conflicts and geopolitical instability .
Third , raise the level of trade liberalization and facilitation
We will steadily promote trade liberalization and facilitation and accelerate the signing of the SCO Trade Facilitation Agreement .
Fourth , the construction of a fast and convenient Unicom pattern .
Fifth , promote the in-depth development of production capacity and innovation cooperation .
Sixth , tie up the ties of human exchange and cooperation .
Li stressed that since this year , China's economy has shifted to a stage of high-quality development , which will bring new opportunities for cooperation between China and the SCO countries .
China will link its own development with regional national development and integrate its own security with regional national security .
On December 1 local time , Premier Li Keqiang of the State Council met with Russian Prime Minister Dmitri Medvedev and Kyrgyz Prime Minister Isaacov in Sochi respectively .
We will continue to play the role of the SCO as a platform to contribute wisdom and strength to the joint building of a regional destiny community and the promotion of open , inclusive development and lasting peace in the world .
During the meeting with Isaacov , Li said he hoped the two sides would continue to follow the principle of marketization and speed up cooperation on cross-border transport infrastructure construction .
During the meeting with Kobiyakov , Li Keqiang expressed the hope that the two sides would further strengthen the strategic docking of development , give full play to their complementary advantages and tap the potential of economic , trade and investment cooperation .
Mr Kobiyakov said the White side would participate in the International Import Expo to be held in China next year , and hoped that the year 2018 would be designated as the White-China Tourism Year , and expand tourism cooperation and youth exchanges .
During the meeting with Sagintaev , Li Keqiang expressed the hope that China and Kazakhstan will continue to work together .
Implementation of the consensus already reached
And strengthen the carding of relevant results and experience , promote pragmatic cooperation between the two sides , especially capacity cooperation to move forward at a greater pace .
Sagintaev said that Kazakhstan is ready to actively implement the important consensus reached by the leaders of the two countries and create favorable conditions for further cooperation in production capacity .
During the meeting with Abdullah , Li Keqiang said that China supports the efforts of the Afghan Government of National Unity to safeguard national security and stability .
We will work together to build a stable and secure regional environment and promote the achievement of long-term stability in the region at an early date
