Yesterday , the cash loan standard reorganization plan released , will exist to the cash loan excessive borrowing , repeated credit , improper collection
High interest rates , invasion of personal privacy and other prominent issues vigorously rectify .
The new regulations make it clear that no organization or individual may engage in the lending business without obtaining the qualifications for operating the lending business in accordance with the law .
Provisions on interest rates for private loans .
All types of institutions or agencies entrusted to third parties shall not be subjected to violence , intimidation , insult , defamation , harassment or other means
Suspension of the new batch of small-sum loan companies across provinces , districts and cities to carry out small-sum loan business
Where the preparation has been approved , the opening of business shall be suspended
For approved bodies that do not comply with the relevant requirements
The scheme also regulates the off-balance-sheet financing of small loan companies and the participation of licensed financial institutions in cash loan behavior .
