But in some areas
Does this civilian service stop because of the uncivilized behavior of others
Managers everywhere made a choice
On the one hand through the civilization prompt advocates the economy , on the other hand also carries on the technical innovation .
Public toilets in Nanjing , Suicheng and other places in Jiangsu Province
Brush your face for three seconds to get a free toilet paper , but to get a double , you need to wait another ten minutes
Avoid misuse of public resources
Habit , maybe some tourists do want to put the paper back , but on the other hand we also have to reflect
Is there no paper for the next toilet that our visitors are going to enter , so this is what we have highlighted in our new three-year plan
This imbalance should be resolved properly
