After the welcoming ceremony , Li Keqiang and Trudo held the second annual dialogue between the Prime Minister of China and Canada .
Li Keqiang made positive comments on the development of China-Canada relations over the past year
Li Keqiang said that the current economic globalization continued to advance , a new round of science and technology and industrial revolution swept the whole world
In order to continue healthy and stable development , China-Canada relations must conform to the trend of the times
Adhere to mutual respect , treating each other on an equal footing , mutual benefit and win-win progress , and constantly expand common interests .
Li Keqiang pointed out that China-Canada pragmatic cooperation and complementary strong , should expand two-way trade investment , encourage enterprises of the two countries to invest in each other's countries
Li stressed that China and Canada are both important countries in the Asia-Pacific region and major trading countries in the world , and it is in the common interest of both sides to send positive signals on the issue of promoting trade and investment liberalization and facilitation .
The door of China's opening to the outside world will be bigger and bigger , the business environment will be better and better , and will continue to be a hot ground for international investment .
Continue the friendship between the two countries
Canada supports free trade and is ready to work with China to promote globalization and free trade and contribute to global sustainable development .
The two sides also exchanged views on international and regional issues of common concern .
After the talks , the two Prime Ministers jointly witnessed the signing of bilateral cooperation documents in the fields of education , food safety and energy .
On the afternoon of the 4th , Li Keqiang and Canadian Prime Minister Trudo met with reporters .
Li Keqiang introduced the results of the second China-Canada Prime Minister's annual dialogue .
He said the two sides agreed to promote the process of globalization , safeguard trade and investment liberalization and facilitation , and are ready to work together to explore the feasibility of the China-Canada Free Trade Agreement .
China is open to the process and content of the negotiations .
The two sides agreed to strengthen tourism and aviation cooperation and close cultural exchanges between the two countries .
Share opportunities , meet challenges together , promote China-Canada relations in the golden stage of constantly flashing light .
We will deepen cooperation in all fields , commit ourselves to common development and prosperity and build a stable and active relationship in the medium and long term .
Chairman of the Standing Committee of the National People's Congress , Zhang Dejiang 4 , attended the 4th National Constitution Day Symposium and delivered a speech
He stressed that in-depth study should be carried out to carry out the thought of socialism with Chinese characteristics in the new era of Xi Jinping
As a top priority in learning and carrying out the spirit of the 19th National Congress of the Party , the Central Committee of the Party , with Comrade Xi Jinping at its core , has fully implemented the major decision-making arrangements on strengthening the implementation and supervision of the Constitution
We will more firmly and consciously abide by the principles of the Constitution , carry forward the spirit of the Constitution , fulfill the mission of the Constitution , and make better use of the Constitution to build a well-off society in an all-round way
An important role in building a modern socialist country in an all-round way .
Zhang Dejiang pointed out that the Constitution is the fundamental law of the state and the general constitution governing the state .
We must vigorously carry forward the spirit of the Constitution , implement the Constitution in an all-round way , and unswervingly adhere to the leadership of the Communist Party of China
We will firmly safeguard the core position of General Secretary Xi Jinping , firmly uphold the authority of the Party Central Committee and centralized and unified leadership , and unswervingly adhere to socialism with Chinese characteristics
Conversion to the conscious actions of all the people
Zhang Dejiang stressed that in-depth constitutional publicity and education is an important basic work to promote the rule of law in an all-round way , as well as a long-term task .
We must continue to play an important role in the activities of the National Constitution Day and the swearing-in of the Constitution , and make more use of the way that the people like to see and hear
We will carry out publicity and education in the Constitution , strive to improve the quality of the rule of law of the whole nation , build a solid ideological foundation for the implementation of constitutional law and create a good social environment .
To establish the sense of constitution , enhance the self-confidence of the Constitution , become a firm believer , speaker , practitioner and defender of the Constitution .
